{"tid":1989202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國FCC發通牒 有意把中國電信商逐出美國","createTime":"2020-04-25T18:05:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T03:29:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e0693f3a5324bc8d0d673a0cf5b0c41d5dc714d3","tid":1989202,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:05:56.000Z","msg":"美國FCC發通牒 有意把中國電信商逐出美國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3145454\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3145454&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=127fa80c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3145454&h=a3ba094d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3145454</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕美國聯邦通訊委員會（FCC）於24日發函給中國電信、中國聯通在美國營運的子公司，以及中國中信集團在美國營運的子公司Pacific Networks Corp、ComNet （USA） LLC等，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要求這些公司解釋「為何FCC不應該採取行動，廢除這些公司在美國營運執照」，強烈暗示FCC有意將中國電信業者逐出美國。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n據《路透》報導，FCC的發函，指的是與中國政府有關的，對美國電腦入侵等駭客行為所造成的傷害；FCC主席派伊（Ajit Pai）在新聞稿中就表示：「談到電信網路安全的時候，我們不能冒險，我的也希望能有最好的。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">FCC表示，這些公司自10幾年前獲准進入美國以來，「與中國政府舉動有關的國安及執法方面的風險，已經顯著增加。」</span></span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，FCC的發函已經表明，FCC有意以「國家安全」為由，廢除這些中國「國有」電信商在美國的營運牌照，也反映了美國自川普就任總統以來，對中國採取的強硬路線。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，美國司法部等聯邦政府部門在本月的時候，就已呼籲FCC把中國電信的營運執照給廢照，而FCC也在去年5月一致否決了中國移動的美國營運許可，理由是中國政府可能藉此刺探美國政府。"},{"pid":"e636c959f9c281c1bf496dc57c6ff4fb8acbf1f7","tid":1989202,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:18:05.000Z","msg":"扼住支共喉舌講假話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/fcc-may-halt-u-s-operations-of-three-state-controlled-chinese-telecom-firms-20200425/5391852.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Ffcc-may-halt-u-s-operations-of-three-state-controlled-chinese-telecom-firms-20200425%2F5391852.html&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCgmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=e02134fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/fcc-may-halt-u-s-operations-of-three-state-controlled-chinese-telecom-firms-20200425/5391852.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3d5c7f4ce93b44ea1e4c38d3bed86a378b603f","tid":1989202,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a7f05c47d8fc26c63a380df5acc3dcd32b0947","tid":1989202,"uid":199957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:18:38.000Z","msg":"好明顯要啦中國有冇開放電訊市場？ 既然佢自己個家唔開放嘅話點解其他國家要開放畀佢"},{"pid":"dcd8c44fa6f21f128d0bd66493fd14bffb4178b0","tid":1989202,"uid":28223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T20:27:32.000Z","msg":"重要禁止支共收購任何企業 唔係又死灰復燃"},{"pid":"a52d3b04afe476398e39d9b28e4a1f89f99e9e48","tid":1989202,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T02:33:36.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09dc59e7a92127a7f9d465196b02ce9a2f72498","tid":1